{"tid":1961008,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍又撞山死　演練「突擊香港」 軍機撞山11人死","createTime":"2020-04-06T13:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T13:41:46.000Z","uid":261647,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"65d2011509c6e6cd91de58f7b293a0feb8c97e4e","tid":1961008,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T13:11:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2962643\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2962643&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2lexmaKe8vvTAxx9uYoYxOzRs%3D&h=5ecc4656\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2962643&h=caa2714a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2962643</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2019/10/31/phpBs45Wh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2019%2F10%2F31%2FphpBs45Wh.jpg&h=33cc46f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n解放軍進行千里外「突襲香港」演習，其中一架直升機撞山墜毀，機上11人身亡。圖為中共建政70週年，解放軍在空中排出「70」畫面。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕根據香港媒體消息，這是解放軍進行千里外「突襲香港」演習時，其中一架最新型的運輸直升機直-8G撞山墜毀，造成機上11人全部罹難。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港《中國人權民運信息中心》 報導，解放區南部戰區第75集團軍「第121空中突擊旅」，進行「突擊香港」演習，把湖南省漵浦縣假設為「香港」，空中突擊旅的直升機從800公里外的廣西崇左市出發展開突擊。<br />\n<br />\n晚間7點多，一架直-8G直升機在漵浦縣撞山，機上11名解放軍全部身亡，其中包括3名駕駛軍官、8名士兵。"},{"pid":"7c2aec8ac614b2e37d832d4beb07526b2f9be19d","tid":1961008,"uid":47042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T13:13:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Old News <br />\nBlock </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不推文</span></span>"},{"pid":"d0386b1cdb952a04c81a6f65faab9ed0574451eb","tid":1961008,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T13:13:20.000Z","msg":"2019-10-31 08:43:07"},{"pid":"54371b117f